title: When will the season end?
body: Hello I know it ends today, November 7th. But does it end today at midnight? or is it already over? please let me know.

replies.body: The 2017 season ends November 7th at 23:59 Pacific Time, and you can keep track of it with the [**Ranked Rewards Help Desk Countdown**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk?sort_type=recent#comments) ^_^
